metadata.name: Magic island Ometepe
metadata.description:
Triangles🔺, circles🟡, eyeballs👁, waves🌊, fire volcano🌋🔥, volcano with a lake in the crater🗻, portals🌀, cycles🌒🌕🌘, rebirths🔮, growth🌱, falls🍂, healing🥰, opening🤗 and feeling all of this on the absolutely magical island Ometepe.

I just transformed the moments into the lines and drew my impression of this magical place.
